<br>
First off, I would like to thank you for allowing me to join HoS.  While leveling with no guild tag, I received several offers to join other fine guilds, but because of RL friends, I decided to wait and just continue leveling so I could once again join them in a guild and I am glad I did.  <br>
<br>
In the 1st 2 weeks in HoS, I have not been very active due in large part to trying to obtain the Glowing Wurm Biles for the 5th shawl.  I am using my druid (Kellmon) to kite the worms around, which is very boring and tedious.  However, if you need the services of a cleric for a group or ress, or if you need a port from a level 43 druid, please feel free to look me up and send me a tell.  <br>
<br>
Safe Travels All,<br>
<br>
Frede<br>
