<br>
I have actually been kiting in that very area and as a dark elf with night vision, I have been able to see a few of the worms that glow.  Unfortunalty, there are usually a few others out there killing em as well so getting to the glowing ones first has been a problem. I also really hate asking people to, in essence, stop what they are doing and dump their time in to something for me unless I absolutly have to.  While it will take a bit of time to get 4 more biles, hoping none fail, I can get them.  In the past, Brigg has been kind enough to help kill worms and Aylina has also said she would help in the future.<br>
<br>
I have the tailoring up to 124 and will be heading back into Velks to get a few more threads and lots more of the silks to try and bump the tailoring up farther before I try and combine them.  <br>
